flowchart TD
    Start([package unlink package app]) --> ParseArgs[Parse package name and app]
    ParseArgs --> BuildPath[Build app path in ~/projects/]
    
    BuildPath --> CheckApp{App dir exists?}
    CheckApp -->|No| AppNotFound[Error: App not found]
    AppNotFound --> FailExit([Failure])
    
    CheckApp -->|Yes| RunUnlink[Run composer unlink in app dir]
    RunUnlink --> CheckResult{Success?}
    
    CheckResult -->|Yes| ReportSuccess[Report package unlinked]
    ReportSuccess --> SuccessExit([Success])
    
    CheckResult -->|No| UnlinkError[Error: Failed to unlink]
    UnlinkError --> FailExit
